{"tid":668192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲肥婆咁多腳毛？","createTime":"2018-05-17T11:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T13:52:07.000Z","uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec27b781cd3c2519aae3e087f1fd867aabd3b69","tid":668192,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ebbb857237606df744de2f52f2de93602b9a42","tid":668192,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:34:11.000Z","msg":"我瘦都好多腳毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805fb97e8827052b466ebfd143bb2f6d8a6cf4f1","tid":668192,"uid":109491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"文呢"},{"pid":"ba01bbcb687ec9439a9526603053f4c96f9c6a8e","tid":668192,"uid":22589,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"下身方面又係有學問，肥婆食咁多漢堡包同牛肉，男性荷爾蒙分泌過盛。 <br />\n所以塊西至屎o全部都係毛，無論佢幾乾淨，都有陣咸魚溝變壞乳酪嘅味道。 <br />\n據英國研究，82.5%肥婆都唔會剃腳毛，因為烏低身嗰下等於做sit up，有違肥人忠旨。 <br />\n所以肥婆啲腳毛永遠好似鐵線咁粗。 <br />\n奶西嘅時候叫佢瞓低你忠個頭埋去，兩隻手要掃佢隻腳啲鐵線等佢起雞皮，然後叫佢嗰對火腿夾實自己個頭唔好比空氣流出。 <br />\n陣咸魚味喺真空環境會得到昇華，係有層次而漸進的。"},{"pid":"cd05140f057bf1859f5e90acd3168888234be59a","tid":668192,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"@S_Kagawa"},{"pid":"4db98c48cefa8ca320908cbc8afd80707e41e7b3","tid":668192,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd05140f057bf1859f5e90acd3168888234be59a","tid":668192,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"@S_Kagawa"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:50:57.000Z","msg":"你好25"},{"pid":"6cf0282a4598df86ec9ecf3cf028dd49a37804ca","tid":668192,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4db98c48cefa8ca320908cbc8afd80707e41e7b3","tid":668192,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo